title: Tribute band to rock at Wolverhampton gig
text:
PUBLISHED: September 30, 2015 11:22 am LAST UPDATED: September 30, 2015 2:56 pm Tribute band to rock at Wolverhampton gig An all-female tribute to rockers AC/DC will come to Wolverhampton next month. The Robin 2 in Bilston 
Back:N:Black will play Bilston’s Robin 2 for a Halloween special on October 31. Founded in 2010, the band consists of five young female musicians. 
Tickets are £12.50 in advance or £15 on the door. 
Call the box office on 01902 401211 or book online at www.therobin.co.uk. Receive daily email updates from the Express & Star
